						               													<description>Tombstone is a 127 page rulebook for skirmish games using an old west setting. Games typically use around 8-15 models a side and a game takes a couple of hours. Choose from 6 factions, Lawmen, Outlaws, Mexicans, Natives, 7th Cavalry or Undead. We also produce a range of female gunfighters to be used within an existing faction or on their own.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Games can be played as a one off or as part of a campaign system detailed within the book. Gangs can improve skills, stats, buy new weapons and recruits and also sustain injuries or die.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is for use with miniatures in the 28-40mm sizes. We recently launched a succesful kickstarter for the book and over 100 new miniatures which will all be released in the coming months, faction by faction. It's also completely compatible with our extensive existing range.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
